    <entry>
      <title>搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="2021/04/30/23941.html"/>
      <url>2021/04/30/23941.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li>安装node.js</li></ol><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1jxa9e6fj30h80ccdgu.jpg" alt="image-20210430101612677"></p><ol start="2"><li>检验是否安装成功</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1k2x2w9zj307c021mx5.jpg" alt="image-20210430102137966"></p><ol start="3"><li>更换淘宝镜像源</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1k3xrqp1j30fl0393yz.jpg" alt="image-20210430102236390"></p><ol start="4"><li>检查是否更换成功</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1k5301jcj30fp03qt93.jpg" alt="image-20210430102342035"></p><ol start="5"><li>安装hexo框架</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1k5z6zyyj30fm091wg2.jpg" alt="image-20210430102434333"></p><ol start="6"><li>检查是否安装成功</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1k6staooj309i07dgm0.jpg" alt="image-20210430102521607"></p><ol start="7"><li>建立一个空的文件夹</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir blog </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="8"><li>进入blog</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd blog/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="9"><li>初始化hexo,搭建博客</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kfzj4ekj30ix09tq3r.jpg" alt="image-20210430103411000"></p><ol start="10"><li>启动博客</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kh4tq47j30f102mwer.jpg" alt="image-20210430103517852"></p><p>发现在本地的localhost:4000端口启动</p><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kkw42jdj30uy0goqba.jpg" alt="image-20210430103853158"></p><ol start="11"><li>新建第一篇博客文章</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;我的第一篇博客文章&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kk8ar4fj30f8021aab.jpg" alt="image-20210430103815888"></p><ol start="12"><li>根据路径查看是否存在</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/Users/liuguangquan/blog/source/_posts/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kmosngwj30be01c3yl.jpg" alt="image-20210430104038263"></p><ol start="13"><li>利用vim打开添加内容</li></ol><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kqf5boij30fu0abgm1.jpg" alt="image-20210430104412905"></p><ol start="14"><li>清理，生成</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kt1yfcsj30bg0653z9.jpg" alt="image-20210430104644951"></p><ol start="15"><li>把博客推送到github上</li></ol><p>登陆账号，新建仓库</p><p>注意：仓库名必须与用户名一致</p><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1kzdzmlkj30i203tmxh.jpg" alt="image-20210430105250251"></p><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1l58rvlqj30wv0k9tci.jpg" alt="image-20210430105827053"></p><ol start="16"><li>安装git插件</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1l1im164j30fn031jrq.jpg" alt="image-20210430105452842"></p><ol start="17"><li>设置_config.yml</li></ol><ul><li>进入底部有个deploy</li></ul><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1l3grfzwj30a901lwei.jpg" alt="image-20210430105645142"></p><ul><li>修改type</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>添加repo</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repo: https://github.com/echo-machile/echo-machile.github.io.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>添加branch</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1l824odij30e403saaa.jpg" alt="image-20210430110110262"></p><ol start="18"><li>将博客部署到远端</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="19"><li>访问博客</li></ol><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1mfbju69j30xo0jvwpj.jpg" alt="image-20210430114241934"></p><ol start="20"><li>修改博客样式</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git themes/yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>编辑_config.yml文件</li></ul><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1mqdvq1cj30f10473yu.jpg" alt="image-20210430115317612"></p><ul><li><p>找到theme修改为yilia，保存退出</p></li><li><p>清理，生成，开启</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gq1mszjhu4j30xr0g1gmz.jpg" alt="image-20210430115548362"></p><ol start="21"><li>推送到远端</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> blog </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
